COPS have arrested five people found with lots of SASSA cards and cash. Captain Namhla Mdlelen said a joint operation which inluded OCC members, Flying Squad and Crime Prevention led to the arrest of five suspects in possession of Sassa cards and undisclosed amount of money. Madlelen said cops received information of suspected people carrying lot of Sassa cards and quickly responded to the information. All suspects were arrested and were due to appear before Queenstown Magistrate Court on Friday.